*{{flagcountry|Barbados}} (1982)
*{{flagcountry|Dominica}} (1982)
*{{flagcountry|Grenada}} (1985)
*{{flagcountry|Saint Kitts and Nevis}} (1983)
*{{flagcountry|Saint Lucia}} (1982)
*{{flagcountry|Saint Vincent and the Grenadines}} (1982)

